| Severity | Count | Top Issue |
|----------|-------|-----------|
| 🔴 Critical | 0 | — |
| 🟡 Moderate | 6 | Chained regex Replace + substring allocations in hot-path methods |
| ℹ️ Info | 1 | Unsealed class |

